summary: Admin introductions! Admin Kuroo Heyo, I’m Kuroo. Currently I’m the only artist and coder in the project. I help write some of...
body:
Admin introductions!

Admin Kuroo

Heyo, I’m Kuroo. Currently I’m the only artist and coder in the project. I help write some of the story/plot/ideas along with Yaku. I’m glad I get to draw Tomura’s emo band™

Admin Yaku

Yo I’m Yaku and I’m the main writer, help find the music for the game, and help brainstorm ideas. I write basically everything- routes, where to put in the art, choices, etc- and Kuroo codes it and draws it. I have a lot of fun writing the scripts, finding awesome music, and brainstorming ideas
